sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User device
    participant W as wifi_task
    participant C as control_task
    participant S as comm_task snapshot

    U->>W: Connect to SoftAP
    U->>W: GET /
    W-->>U: HTML dashboard

    loop Dashboard refresh
        U->>W: GET /api/data
        W->>S: Read sensor snapshot
        W->>C: Read water state and profile
        W-->>U: JSON response
    end

    opt User changes profile
        U->>W: POST /api/fan
        W->>C: Update active profile
    end
